    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Shi Hou Clan, Level 16+</p><p>You can temporarily enter a perfect mindset, and truly reach the level of the great Heavenly Sage. You gain the following benefits;</p><p>• Once per long rest, as an action, you can spend 5 Inner Chi and enter this heavenly state. While transformed you cannot cast nor concentrate on ninjutsu or genjutsu, and at the start of each of your turns you must spend 1 Inner Chi to maintain the transformation. You gain the following benefits;</p><p>o All Taijutsu (and Bukijutsu, if you have the Legacy of Heroes feat) you cast gain the benefit from both effects of your Inner Chi feature. If the jutsu possess multiple attack rolls, each attack benefits from the additional damage dice.</p><p>o You add 1d10 to all strength and dexterity skill checks you make.</p><p>o You can use 72 Earthly Transformations as part of taking the attack action.</p><p>• Reduce the cost of all 72 Earthly Transformations by half. Simple Transformations cost 0 Inner Chi to activate.</p>",
